Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩认识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So you two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟哈罗德是麻省理工的同学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Harold and I go all the way back to M.I.T.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说肿瘤让他的记忆如洪水般涌出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He said his tumor was causing memories to flood out at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有第二台机器  亚瑟造的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There was a second machine, and Arthur built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道有谁想要伤害你丈夫吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Do you know of anyone who'd want to hurt your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Vigilance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这是不可避免了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I suppose this was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主控者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们中会有人开口告诉我我想知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}One of you is gonna tell me what it is I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们多走运啊  赫什探员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How lucky are we, Agent Hersh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为要找亚瑟坏掉的玩具  "撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I thought I was getting Arthur's broken toy, Samaritan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but you, Harold...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你是谁  为我们做过什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I know who you are, what you've done for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从你偷了我们的装置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but since you stole my device,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直担心我们的情报会断源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've been worried its intel might dry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就对亚瑟做出这种事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's why you've done these terrible things to Arthur,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抹去他妻子的身份  窃取她的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}obliterated his wife's identity, stolen her life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了当应急预案  后备计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All for a contingency, a plan "B"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在你在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But now you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.18,0:01:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后备计划可能就不需要了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A plan "B" might not be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以告诉我把我的程序藏到哪儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You can tell me where you hid my program.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  它自己搬走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't know. It moved itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不属于我了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It doesn't answer to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先开口的  就能活着离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The first one to talk gets to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你朋友最终会交出"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I bet your friend will give me Samaritan eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会2005年叫停了"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Congress shut down Samaritan in 2005,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁掉了编码  它不存在了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}destroyed the code-- it doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它当然存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Of course it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Please, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉过我你采取了预防措施\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You told me you took precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,销毁"撒马利亚人"时丢了两块硬盘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Two drives disappeared during the Samaritan purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的大脑无法获取正确的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can't access the right file.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在努力了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经损坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要点强化措施了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We'll need some enhanced methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫什探员  你有什么想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Agent Hersh, do you have some ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖探员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Agent Shaw...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欣赏你工作时的情景令人激动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it has been a thrill watching you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦两枪爆头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Two to the head, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心溅血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And be careful of the blood spray.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arthur!
