Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉过你  哈罗德  我们应该合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I told you, Harold--we were supposed to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后再骂他  根  给我松开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Scold him later, Root. Cut me loose.
