Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也得分了  [拳王]霍利菲尔德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I won my points, Holyfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不把我们弄出去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Are you getting us out of here?
