Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就奇怪这玩意儿为什么不管用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was wondering why that thing didn't work.
