Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么可以帮你的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Can I help you with anything?
