Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来看保险箱  注册名字是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We're here for a safe deposit box in the name of--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯穆特  鲁迪格・斯穆特  保险箱号433\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Smoot. Rudiger Smoot, box 433.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  斯穆特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Of course, Mr. Smoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边走  先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This way, gentlemen.
