Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一只来一针[兴奋剂]安非他明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}An amphetamine in the other--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉如云霄飞车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A roller coaster of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你承受不了几轮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You can only take so many rounds of it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心脏就要爆掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}before your heart explodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Shall we begin?
