Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你碰不着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}beyond your reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你主掌大权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You think you're in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是错得离谱到可爱啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's adorable just how wrong you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的保险箱在这边  斯穆特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your safe deposit box is just over here, Mr. Smoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁迪格・斯穆特是哪根葱啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who the hell is Rudiger Smoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was a dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟说我做不出一个安全到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arthur said I couldn't create a false identity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足以开银行账户的假身份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}sound enough to open a bank account.
