Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}Rudiger是麻省理工当时的名教授\NSmoot是非标准的长度单位  麻省理工学生的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁迪格・斯穆特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Rudiger Smoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁迪格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Rudiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昵称"鲁迪"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Nickname "Rudy"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是克雷普被注射了硫喷妥钠时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The one Claypool was dishing about to Vigilance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对"时刻警惕"说出的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}while he was jacked up on sodium pentothal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他告诉了"时刻警惕"地址  只怕很快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If he told Vigilance the location, we'll soon have
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些咄咄逼人的隐私激进分子就要来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}some rather aggressive privacy activists on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比"很快"还快  已经来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sooner than soon. We got company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在用激光破坏安保摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They're using tricked-out lasers to fry the security cams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是"时刻警惕"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's Vigilance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来拖住他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll slow 'em down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  请把钥匙给我  斯穆特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Here we are. I'll need your key, Mr. Smoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖趴下  免得受伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Get down and no one gets hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人马上趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Everybody down on the ground right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们听到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You heard him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下  我不会再重复了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Down, now! I'm not gonna tell you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直说银行开了就是用来抢的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've always said banks were meant to be robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去左边  快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}To the left! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们听到了  快  快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You heard him! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到后面去  继续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All the way back! Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突击队来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The cavalry has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安东尼  左边两个  右边两个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Anthony, 2 left, 2 right--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是赫什  马上出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's Hersh. Get out of there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下武器  举起手从银行出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Drop your weapons and come out of the bank with your hands up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去组织防线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll organize the defensive line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  我去金库\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Good. I'll go to the vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇  快出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Finch, get out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚了  祝你好运  肖女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Too late. Good luck, Ms. Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很快就得放我们出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They got to let us out of here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在关着我们就当笑话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They're just keeping us in here for a laugh at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监狱也没什么不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Nothing wrong with jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最好的几个假期都是在监狱里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Some of the best vacations I've ever had were behind bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是人见人爱花见花开  知道不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're a peach, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想办法出去  然后回家吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How about we just figure a way to get out of here and go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么家  莱奈尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What home, Lionel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的  虽然你从没邀请我去过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You know, I mean, you've never actually invited me over,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but home--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们的朋友  我们做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}meaning our friends and that thing we were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做的什么事呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What is it we were doing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Helping people,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护他们的安全  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}keeping 'em safe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们能回家与挚爱团圆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}so they could get home to their loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无意冒犯  莱奈尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No offense, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道"当好人"这种事对你来说很新鲜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I know the whole "being a good guy" thing is new to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你谁也骗不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but you're not fooling anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都骗不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and neither will we.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是在帮助别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We weren't helping people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是推迟了"必然"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We were delaying the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人说过我们一定会赢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No one ever said we were gonna win,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这不代表要放弃抗争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but it doesn't mean you stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经接受了教训\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've learned my lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像熵  莱奈尔  会衰退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's entropy, Lionel, decay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们救了人  人家依旧会死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We save someone, they'll still lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是明天  不是今天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}just tomorrow, not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I know that now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我明白你多半会回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}same as I know you'll probably go back
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变回腐败的人渣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to be a corrupt piece of garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水往低处流啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Water finds its level.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道么  她是我们中最好的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You know what? She was the best of us--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我好  更他妈比你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Better than me and a damn sight better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而她却被杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And she got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where I come from,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不是放弃的理由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that doesn't mean you just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯基普  我们谈完了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Skip! We're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱去哪去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱干嘛干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会告诉芬奇我尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll tell Finch I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tell Finch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢他给我这份工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}thanks for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨晚起就没再收到眼镜儿的消息了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I haven't heard from Glasses since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不像他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's not like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能需要我们的帮助了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He probably needs our help,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过无济于事  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but there's no point, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是在推迟"必然"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We'd just be delaying the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她的腿抬高  继续压住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Elevate her leg. Continue applying pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能这样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You've done all you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压好  我们不会走远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Keep this. We won't be far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟  跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arthur, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖女士  你那边情况如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Ms. Shaw, what's your situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进退两难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Rock and a hard place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以干掉"时刻警惕"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'd take out Vigilance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只有他们才能阻止赫什进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but they're the only ones keeping Hersh out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概能单独搞定一个突击小组\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can probably handle an I.S.A. tac team by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不能保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but no guarantees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要逃脱路线  但你必须小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We need an escape route, but you have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我强烈要求你考虑下里瑟先生会怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I urge you to consider what Mr. Reese would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉思吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Brood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所说  你就像锤子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}As you've said, you're a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里瑟先生则像手术刀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Reese is a scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时需要精巧处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This requires a bit more finesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精巧于我如屁  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I got finesse coming out of my ass, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在那\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在想你什么时候会打来呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was wondering when you'd call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事没必要闹大  大家都能活着出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This doesn't have to escalate. Everyone can walk out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  别耍花样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Come on, no need to play games.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们心里都清楚我不是银行劫匪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We both know I'm not a bank robber
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不是人质谈判专家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and you're not a hostage negotiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们六十秒内撤走  我留你们条活路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If you evacuate in the next 60 seconds, we'll let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则  你的组织会被彻底消灭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If not, your organization ceases to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无声无息  死无葬身之地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No records, no funerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本来也没打算让我们活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You have no intention of letting us leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过很高兴我们通话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but I'm glad we talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到消息说硬盘里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My sources tell me the drives
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有关于一个全球监视系统的情报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}hold intel about a worldwide surveillance system,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看你这紧张的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but judging from your concern,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜里面的东西更具爆炸性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm guessing it's something even more explosive than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得为之去死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}something worth dying for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会曝光政府的恶行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We will expose the abuses our government has perpetrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别了  探员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Good-bye, Agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府想要一个开放系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The government wanted an open system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让国安局能够控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That the N.S.A. could control...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随意监控任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}targeting individuals at whim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这已经坏掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But it's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么可担心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So there's no reason to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Harold...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}meet Samaritan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人工智能  你总说不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A.I.--you always said it was impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你总是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and you were always right about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有其他东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界会打击每一个人  但经历过后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"The world breaks everyone, and afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人会在受伤的地方变得更加强大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}many are strong at the broken places."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[海明威小说]《永别了武器》  是我的笔迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A Farewell To Arms-- that's my handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日期写着2005年2月24日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's dated February 24, 2005.
