Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没想出来  不过看我的书法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I haven't the foggiest, but look at my penmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多优美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以让这一切停止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You have the power to make this stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我  求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Help me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帮你啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I am trying to help you.
