Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说  机器在哪儿  如何进入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tell me, where is the machine? How do you access it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要给我用户名和密码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All you need to do is give me your username and password.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切就可以停止了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All of this could stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了什么好笑的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Did I say something funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本没有问到点子上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're asking all the wrong questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是界面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}am the interface.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想和她说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If you want to talk to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我个电话就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Just give me a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可以吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我腾不出手了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm sorry. I'm--I'm a bit tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还不能给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're not gonna get it just yet.
