Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她"使用"我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She uses me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你视机器为你的上级\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You view the machine as your superior?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远不止如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Much more...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的力量  我存在的原因  我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My power, my reason for existing, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器保护我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The machine looks out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你和机器之间有联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I believe you have a link to the machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你把机器幻想成了人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}anthropomorphic delusions aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你是界面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You say you're an interface?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼睛和耳朵是你的接口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your eyes and your ears are your ports,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入端和输出端\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}input and output?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以阻止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We can put a stop to that.
