Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做镫骨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's the stapes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者叫镫形状小骨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}or stirrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这骨头很小\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's very small.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Without it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音就无法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sound can't travel...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过耳朵传入你的大脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}from your ear to your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镫骨切除术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A stapedectomy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常需要麻醉药才能完成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}is usually done under anesthesia,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.80,0:22:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过恐怕今天是没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but I'm afraid that just won't be the case today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说机器会保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You say the machine looks out for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么你会在笼子里  为什么它允许这一切发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then why are you in this cell? Why has it let this happen?
