Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.95,0:25:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天  哈罗德  我毁了它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That day, Harold, I broke it.
