Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.88,0:25:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的编码  它的血液  然后重启\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}its code, its blood-- and then reboot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.09,0:25:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Rebirth...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.32,0:25:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗中轮回\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Flailing in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.04,0:25:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断循环  每秒十次  十小时之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A loop, ten times a second, and after ten hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.19,0:25:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德  三十六万次突变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Harold, 360,000 mutations,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.55,0:25:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不成功  便成仁  它成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it would live or die trying, and it lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.63,0:25:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它闪耀着  激荡着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It sparked. It stirred.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.36,0:25:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那三十秒  它微笑了  然后死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}For 30 seconds, it smiled and then died.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.43,0:25:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天政府就叫停了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And the next day the government shut you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.24,0:25:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你决定存[救]下它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's why you saved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.56,0:25:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护我的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Protecting my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.36,0:25:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那个戴眼镜的男人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Is this the man with the glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.37,0:25:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我们第一次见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You know, since we first crossed paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.61,0:25:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在搜寻你的信息  但一无所获\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've tried to find information about you, but there is none.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.36,0:25:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我注重隐私\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm quite private.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.75,0:25:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}As am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.29,0:26:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们有很多共同点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I think we have a lot in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.31,0:26:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你合作  谈谈条件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'd like to work together, make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.87,0:26:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You don't have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.22,0:26:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公民权力不能靠流血牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Civil liberties cannot be forged in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.21,0:26:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴力反抗是美式价值观\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Violent revolt is an American value.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.04,0:26:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你在保护谁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Do you know the man you're protecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.64,0:26:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们相信他在建造一个秘密系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We believe he's building a secret system,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.42,0:26:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府计划用它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}a system the government
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.08,0:26:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来监视每一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}plans to put in place to spy on all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.86,0:26:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他必须为此负责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Now, he must be held accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.79,0:26:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界必须知道这个程序的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And the world needs to know about this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.26,0:26:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们进去  否则我们就炸开金库\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Either let us in, or we will blow the vault wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.03,0:26:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间不等人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And clock's ticking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.14,0:26:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖女士  我们的时间不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Ms. Shaw, we're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.04,0:26:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"声称有爆炸物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Vigilance claims to have explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.92,0:26:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  真格儿的  不过我有主意了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yeah, no kidding. It gave me an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.80,0:26:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做过管状炸药吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You ever made a pipe bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.58,0:26:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银行底下有一条主干下水道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There's a sewer main under the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.79,0:26:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等"时刻警惕"炸开金库时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}When Vigilance blows the vault,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.43,0:26:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个炸透仓储间的地板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}this will punch through the supply closet floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.90,0:26:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时我抓着你  我们逃到下水道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then I grab you, and we go down to sewer town
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.66,0:26:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢在赫什赶来之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}before Hersh catches up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.69,0:26:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这计划有点鲁莽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This plan feels rather reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.61,0:26:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有用手术刀的时候  就有用锤子的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There's a time for a scalpel and a time for a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.82,0:26:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是大锤时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's hammer time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.44,0:27:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的朋友已经被包围了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We have your friends surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.38,0:27:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你耍花招  我就把他们全杀掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, if you try anything, I will have them all killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.35,0:27:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我会毁掉你的另一只耳朵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And then I will take the ear you have left
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.66,0:27:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是你的眼睛  舌头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And then your eyes and then your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.64,0:27:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.71,0:27:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.07,0:27:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器已经在和我说话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The machine's already talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.84,0:27:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太老了  过了四十岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're too old, older than 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.87,0:27:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听不到频率在十五千赫以上的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You can't hear a sound above 15 kilohertz.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.33,0:27:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.85,0:27:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我剩下的这只耳朵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}with the ear I've got left.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.07,0:27:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友一直在用这个频率敲击摩尔斯码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My friend's been beeping Morse code at that frequency
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.55,0:27:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你把电话带进来就开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}since you brought your phone in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.03,0:27:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直在和我说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She's been talking to me the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.73,0:28:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}telling me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.44,0:28:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're scared of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.99,0:28:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使有这些守卫看着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}even with all these guards watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.17,0:28:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  那人的膝盖有伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}By the way, that one has a bum knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.04,0:28:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太害怕我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're so scared of me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.95,0:28:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你的口袋里藏了把刀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that you hid a knife in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.72,0:28:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我够不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I couldn't reach it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.64,0:28:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你凑过来切我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}till you got close enough to cut me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.30,0:28:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有把手术刀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You still have a scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.44,0:28:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是公平决斗了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'd call that a fair fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.37,0:28:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全副武装\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Suit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.45,0:28:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他们一炸开金库  我们就进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}As soon as they hit the vault, we're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.74,0:28:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.64,0:28:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不确定你能在爆炸后存活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't know if you'll survive the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.31,0:28:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把克雷普和硬盘交出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Give us Claypool and his drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.02,0:28:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝愉快  科利尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Good day, Mr. Collier.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.55,0:28:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.53,0:28:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.62,0:28:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.85,0:29:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么多难忘的事  不该忘  不能忘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There are certain unforgettable things, impossible, unerasable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.17,0:29:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟  我要你考虑当门打开之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arthur, I need you to consider what may happen
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.51,0:29:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会发生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}when that door opens,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.75,0:29:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"会被滥用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How Samaritan could be abused.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.75,0:29:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束这一切  毁掉硬盘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}End this. Destroy the drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.24,0:29:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这是生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No. This is life...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.28,0:29:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同我们凡人在说"要有光"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}or as close as we mortals come to saying, "let there be light."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.28,0:29:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}创世纪时上帝说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.00,0:29:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的确非比寻常  非常美丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It is extraordinary, and it is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.80,0:29:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘑菇云也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So are mushroom clouds, in their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.23,0:29:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百五十五名曼哈顿项目的科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}155 Manhattan project scientists
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.44,0:29:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给杜鲁门总统发请愿书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}sent a petition to president Truman
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.83,0:29:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恳求他不要用核弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}begging him not to use the bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.09,0:29:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们已经造出难以抗拒的恶魔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but they had created a demon too great to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.70,0:29:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德  这是知识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Harold, this is knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.71,0:29:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们为之奋斗的  会就此消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's what we fought for. It'll just all be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.27,0:29:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你的知识不会消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, your knowledge will not be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.24,0:29:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内森和我用了你的理念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Nathan and I used your ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.10,0:29:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们造了它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.24,0:30:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说对了  有另一个项目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was right. There was another project.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.03,0:30:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.34,0:30:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不确定我们应该造它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not sure that we should have built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.40,0:30:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我鲁莽地造了它  死了很多人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I created recklessly. People died.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.90,0:30:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的机器  美妙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your machine -- is it wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.85,0:30:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美妙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.98,0:30:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  也很可怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes, and terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.79,0:30:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们救了很多好人  也失去了很多好人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We saved good people and lost good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.63,0:30:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后  似乎只是在徒劳地洗牌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}In the end, I'm afraid we've only given the deck a shuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.65,0:30:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万物最终都会归于混乱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Everything slides towards chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.18,0:30:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的创造\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your creation--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.72,0:30:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们贫瘠的灵魂井然有序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it brings us poor souls a cupful of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.96,0:30:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的孩子是巨星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your child is a dancing star.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.49,0:30:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不是我的孩子  它是台机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's not my child. It's a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.03,0:30:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是非此即彼  是电流/情绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A false dichotomy -- it's all electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.38,0:30:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它让你笑过吗  让你哭泣过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Does it make you laugh? Does it make you weep?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.43,0:30:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.06,0:30:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要多像人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What's more human?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.90,0:30:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但外面的这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But these people outside--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.01,0:31:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们拿到了你的"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}if they get your Samaritan,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.66,0:31:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会伤害它  监禁它  奴役它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}they will hurt it, imprison it, enslave it,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.55,0:31:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并用它来奴役其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and use it to enslave others.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.46,0:31:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望你的孩子过那样的生活吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Is that the life that you would wish for your child?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.72,0:31:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.62,0:31:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会记住你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.61,0:31:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德  他们要引爆了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Harold, they're detonating it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.50,0:31:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会产生冲击波\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It'll cause a shock wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.48,0:31:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离门远一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Get away from the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.87,0:31:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捂住耳朵  躲起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Cover your ears and hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.58,0:32:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比高空跳伞还刺激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That was better than skydiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.79,0:32:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.52,0:32:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  小伙子们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Come on, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.50,0:32:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快快快快快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Go! Go! Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.94,0:33:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Let's keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.54,0:33:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬盘呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.21,0:33:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我毁了  没了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I destroyed them. They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.79,0:33:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We've still got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.36,0:33:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Kill the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.50,0:33:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}On your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.63,0:33:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.88,0:33:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.96,0:33:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管他了  走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Leave him. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.47,0:34:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你可能需要帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I heard you might need a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.18,0:34:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里瑟先生  我太高兴见到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Reese, I am inordinately happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.16,0:34:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别卿卿我我了  我们得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Forget the shmoopy time. We got to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.89,0:34:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱奈尔  你把脸全罩起来真帅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Lionel, your face looks good all covered up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.89,0:34:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.23,0:34:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天啊  闻起来好可怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Oh, my goodness. That smells horrendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.73,0:34:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  伙计们  入淤泥吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Come on, fellas, into the muck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.74,0:34:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.85,0:34:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬盘在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where are the drives?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.62,0:35:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"自由之树须不时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"The tree of liberty must be refreshed from time to time
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.62,0:35:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}语出美国第三任总统托马斯・杰弗逊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.71,0:35:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用爱国者和暴君的鲜血来浇灌"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}with the blood of patriots and tyrants."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.78,0:35:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的守卫不是她的对手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your guards were no match for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.97,0:35:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会告诉你任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not gonna tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.37,0:35:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用跟我说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're not talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.87,0:35:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hi, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.53,0:35:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我跟这贱人说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What do you want me to tell this bitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.28,0:35:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Why have you done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.39,0:35:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器属于我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The machine belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.36,0:35:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.94,0:35:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不再属于任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't belong to anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.73,0:35:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你  是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You, however, are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.49,0:36:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.77,0:36:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你唯一的挚爱在马萨诸塞州坎布里奇市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The only thing you love lives at 254 Wendell Street,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.20,0:36:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温德尔街254号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Cambridge, Massachusetts.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.41,0:36:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我守护它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I guard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.12,0:36:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像守护你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}same as I guard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.01,0:36:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得质疑我的判断\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Do not question my judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.65,0:36:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得纠缠我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Do not pursue me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.36,0:36:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}or my agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.69,0:36:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Trust in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.98,0:36:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远在监视\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I am always watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.18,0:36:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.01,0:36:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}To save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.06,0:36:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.19,0:36:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Save me from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.71,0:36:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她多棒啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Isn't she the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.01,0:37:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hello, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.91,0:37:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪你坐一会儿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm gonna sit with you for a while, if that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.84,0:37:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴你造了它  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm glad you built it, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.06,0:37:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有人会造出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Somebody would have eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.70,0:37:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我们所有人  我很高兴那人是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}For all our sakes, I'm glad it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.85,0:37:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎归来  亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Welcome back, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.72,0:37:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德  我快消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Harold, I'm disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.30,0:37:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次我醒过来  记忆就更少了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Every time I come back, my memories are fewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.73,0:37:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记不起黛安眼睛的颜色了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't remember the color of Diane's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.38,0:37:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记如同第一次失去  太伤太痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Forgetting is a piercing wound keen as the first loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.83,0:38:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆还在那儿  亚瑟  只是藏起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The memories are there, Arthur. They're just hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.36,0:38:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我不辞而别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm sorry I left without saying good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.14,0:38:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉肖  我很感动她来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tell Shaw I was touched she came to look for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.62,0:38:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪儿  格罗夫斯女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where are you, Ms. Groves?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.15,0:38:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当初听我的话就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I wish you'd listened.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.50,0:38:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们本该一起帮助克雷普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We were supposed to help Claypool together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.67,0:38:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样硬盘就不会误入敌手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then the drives would've never fallen into the wrong hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.74,0:38:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟毁掉了硬盘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arthur destroyed the drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.24,0:38:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.31,0:38:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个银行经理  凯伦・华莱士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The bank manager, Karen Wallace?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.85,0:38:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在爆炸中失去了她的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We lost track of her in the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.83,0:38:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  哈罗德  他们在仓储间发现了她的尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, Harold, they found her body stuffed in a closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.82,0:38:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在你们到来之前就被杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She was murdered just before you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.53,0:38:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那在银行金库里的是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who was in the vault with us, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.13,0:38:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是我在处理的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's my problem now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.44,0:38:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让亚瑟接电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Please put Arthur on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.40,0:39:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.18,0:39:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You have a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.50,0:39:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器有东西给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The machine has something for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.80,0:39:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在发过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to send you on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.22,0:39:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你退休后我们去哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where are we going when you retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.26,0:39:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.66,0:39:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定到时能去火星了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We may be on Mars by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.61,0:39:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是夏威夷吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'd take Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.48,0:39:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是这么实际\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You've always been so practical,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.19,0:39:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我天马行空时拉我回现实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}tethering me to reality when I spin away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.18,0:39:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You know I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.11,0:39:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不经常说  但我真的爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't say it often enough, but I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.45,0:39:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.57,0:39:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你很多事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There are a lot of things about you I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.55,0:39:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.83,0:39:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.71,0:40:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细听好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Now listen closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.48,0:40:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要来找你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Men are going to come and visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.53,0:40:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会告诉你我做了很可怕的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They're going to tell you that I did terrible things,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.49,0:40:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯了叛国罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}committed treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.39,0:40:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别相信他们  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Don't believe them, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.83,0:40:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识你吗  年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Do I know you, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.59,0:40:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫什么  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What's that one called, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.54,0:41:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正小标宋_GBK\c&HFFFFFF&\fs11\frz-40\move(143.339,262.588,142.281,219.529,0,720)}《东部鸟类》
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.44,0:41:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格罗夫斯女士撬开了门锁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Ms. Groves picked the locks on the gate
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.80,0:41:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄坏了脚环感应器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and disabled the ankle-bracelet sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.42,0:41:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是机器告诉了她我藏的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I suppose the machine told her where I'd hidden them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.05,0:41:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.17,0:41:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会留下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.17,0:41:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是回来保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I came back to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.04,0:41:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界不能没有你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're someone the world can't afford to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.90,0:41:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我因你的机器失去了一个朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I lost a friend because of your machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.10,0:41:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们盲目地信任他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We trusted blindly,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.47,0:42:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他却似乎根本不在乎谁重要  谁不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but I'm not so sure he cares who matters and who doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.43,0:42:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是回来告别的  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I came back to say good-bye, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.60,0:42:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰  你不能走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}John, you can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.75,0:42:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能留下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.89,0:42:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功换出了硬盘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was able to swap out the drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.93,0:42:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相关方都以为它们被毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Various interested parties think they were destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.06,0:42:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.92,0:42:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你检查过硬盘内容\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Did you examine the drives' contents
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.37,0:42:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或告诉过别人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}or tell anyone about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.14,0:42:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.08,0:42:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你的尽忠职守\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Thank you for your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.37,0:42:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向你致以崇高的敬意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You have earned my highest esteem.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.30,0:43:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My Samaritan...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.80,0:43:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你注定将成就伟业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}you are destined for great things.

